cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image synthesis. It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it uses text descriptions to generate images. The use of adversarial learning suggests that it may also fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the datasets used in the experiments are related to graphics (cs.GR), which further supports the possibility of this paper belonging to this sub-category.
